    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she should choose some sections from this book to read.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she read from all those people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then became known that we were But before, nobody cared.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If I would have told somebody, you know, nobody would pay attention.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because that didn't mean anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "After the movie came out, then they start-- when the movie came out, Regine said that she wants us-- we should be interviewed.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I said, not from you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So she sent another man from the station.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he called us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he made the interview.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "After this came-- when this came on the air, right away-- the the all-- everybody, everybody start calling.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Regine is our daughter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She's working for WBB--",
      "word_count": 4
